= Licensing Information =

This software package is dedicated to the Public Domain. This includes
all files (code, documentation, ...) shipped with this distribution.

== Exceptions ==

The following files are not considered part of this distribution and are not
dedicated to the Public Domain:
 - driver/hid-wiimote.h
 - driver/hid-wiimote-*.c
 - driver/hid-wiimote.ko: The kernel driver is licensed under the terms of the
                          GPL. This file is only a copy of the current driver.
                          See the xwiimote_kernel repo for driver development.

